    "HTML में `<dd>` तत्व क्या दर्शाता है?"
  ],
  "questionCode": [],
  "explanationProse": [
    "The [`<dd>` element](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dd) defines a description, definition, or value in a description list, used within `<dl>` tags to pair with `<dt>` (_Description Term_).\n\n    This is useful when showing key-value data. Profile information, Settings, and Stats are a common examples."
